OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirefighters' strike       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpostponed after new pay    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Foffer                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The threat of strike action by         
OL,6, firefighters has been put on hold as   
OL,7, union members consider a new pay offer.
OL,9,FDuring talks on Tuesday, fire service  
OL,10,Femployers put forward a revised offer  
OL,11,Fincluding a 7% pay rise.               
OL,13,FThe Fire Brigades Union (FBU) has      
OL,14,Fpostponed announcing strike dates while
OL,15,Fits members are balloted, BBC Radio 4's
OL,16,FToday programme has been told.         
OL,18,FMore than 80% of members who voted     
OL,19,Fbacked strike action when they were    
OL,20,Fballoted in December 2022.             
